State 3 systems in your environment that might use servo motors in its workings?
 Printers
 Servo motors stop and start the print heads precisely on the page as well as move paper along to print multiple rows of text or graphics
 Conveyor Belts
 Servo motors move, stop, and start conveyor belts carrying product along to various stages
 Solar Tracking System
Servo motors adjust the angle of solar panels throughout the day so that each panel continues to face the sun

